text: Raulino Galvao (born 30 September 1888, date of death unknown) was a German field hockey player. He competed in the men's tournament at the 1908 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1888 births Category:Year of death missing Category:German male field hockey players Category:Olympic field hockey players of Germany Category:Field hockey players at the 1908 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Buenos Aires
